#

Turmeric Chicken with Coconut Rice

40 min
$10
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Cuisine:

AmericanThaiAsian

Course:

Main CourseDinner

Tags:

EasyQuickHealthyComfort Food

Description

A flavorful one-pan dish with vibrant turmeric chicken served over creamy coconut rice.

Ingredients

  • chicken breasts: 2 large
  • turmeric powder: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • coconut milk: 1 cup
  • jasmine rice: 1 cup
  • water: 1 cup
  • fresh cilantro: for garnish
